@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

node "Student Laptop" as StudentDevice
cloud "Campus / Internet Network" as Network
node "EduSecure Server" as Server {
  artifact "Vue Frontend"
  artifact "Spring Boot REST API"
  artifact "Crypto Service Layer"
}
database "PostgreSQL\nbcrypt password hashes\nselected records/files protected" as Db

StudentDevice --> Network : HTTPS / TLS 1.3
Network --> Server : encrypted login, submissions, grades
Server --> Db : hashed passwords + protected sensitive metadata

note right of Server
Server verifies bcrypt password hashes,
validates signatures, and creates
integrity-protected audit records.
end note

note right of Db
Passwords are stored as bcrypt hashes.
Selected sensitive content may be protected
with AES-based mechanisms where required
by the artefact design.
end note
@enduml

